page.title: 16WHAT I DO IN FLEETWOOD
page.content: I am a 14 year old girl and my hobbies are the following: I like the pop groups{Duran Duran and{Spandu Ballet.}Their albums are Rio, Seven and the Ragged Tiger, Duran Duran and Arena. Spandau Ballet albums are True and Prade. At night,I go out with my friend called Lisa.We usually go walking on the beach,a disco or sometimes we go for bicycle rides to{Blackpool}and {Hambleton. When I go to disco's they are usually at the Football Club. They start at 6.30 p.m. and end at 10.30 p.m.I like fashion, my favourite outfit is my long black skirt,my red top and my red leather jacket.My favourite television programmes are{Dallas}and{Dynasty. by Angela Dunne aged 14.
